Name: SHIP BEAM IN METRES
Explanation: THE EXTREME WIDTH OF A SHIP, EXPRESSED IN METRES.

Name: LANDING SITE WIDTH IN METRES
Explanation: THE DISTANCE BETWEEN THE SIDES OF THE LANDING SITE PARALLEL TO THE AIRCRAFT'S FLIGHT PATH.

Name: DROP ZONE WIDTH IN METRES
Explanation: THE DISTANCE BETWEEN THE SIDES OF THE DROP ZONE PARALLEL TO THE AIRCRAFT'S FLIGHT PATH.

Name: TOTAL GAP WIDTH, INCLUDING WATERWAY, IN METRES
OVERALL WING SPAN IN METRES
Explanation: GIVES THE OVERALL WIDTH OF AN AIRCRAFT, INCLUDING ITS WINGS, IN METRES. TWO DECIMAL PLACES ARE PERMITTED.

Name: WIDTH OF BEACH IN METRES, 10-9999
Explanation: THE WIDTH OF A BEACH IN METRES FROM 10 -9999.
